  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示ServiceImpl和ServiceNode两端如何各自创建peer，然后通过Channel建立连接。核心是要体现1-1的链路关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ServiceImpl",
        "ServiceNode",
        "Channel",
        "peer",
        "link"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。两端创建的peer需要区分命名吗？比如ServiceImpl这边创建的叫ImplPeer，ServiceNode那边叫NodePeer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ImplPeer",
        "NodePeer",
        "ServiceImpl",
        "ServiceNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就用ImplPeer和NodePeer。两边都用同一个uuid，比如'uuid1'，表示它们是配对的。然后各自去连接Channel。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ImplPeer",
        "NodePeer",
        "Channel",
        "uuid1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画ServiceImpl创建ImplPeer，加上创建成功的note，然后ImplPeer发起connect到Channel。ServiceNode那边对称处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ServiceImpl",
        "ImplPeer",
        "Channel",
        "ServiceNode",
        "NodePeer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接之后，Channel要分别给NodePeer和ImplPeer返回connected消息，表示双向通道就绪。最后加一个note说明这是1-1 link。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Channel",
        "NodePeer",
        "ImplPeer",
        "connected",
        "1-1 link"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，Channel用虚线箭头返回connected给两边。然后我在NodePeer和ImplPeer上方加了一个span note，标注'1-1 link between the 2 peers'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Channel",
        "NodePeer",
        "ImplPeer",
        "connected",
        "note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，ServiceImpl在创建peer之后、连接之前，是不是还要setHandlers？这个步骤别漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ServiceImpl",
        "ImplPeer",
        "setHandlers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确实漏了，我调整一下顺序：create peer之后先setHandlers，然后再connect。这样逻辑更完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ServiceImpl",
        "ImplPeer",
        "setHandlers",
        "connect"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以了，整个流程清晰了：两端各自create peer，ImplPeer这边多了setHandlers，然后都connect到Channel，收到connected后建立1-1 link。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ServiceImpl",
